name: Casque d'Or - Antoine Kombouare x Momentum

metadata.name: Casque d'Or #1
metadata.description:
Antoine Kombouaré – Casque d'Or

It was the 96th minute in the quarter finals of the UEFA cup, 1993. PSG vs. Real Madrid. The sting of having lost the first match 3–1 still fresh.

In a moment of intense emotion, Antoine Kombouaré scores the goal putting PSG into the semi-finals.

For Kombouaré, it was life-changing. For the club’s fans, it was life-changing, too. The game was voted the best in the history of the club.
